---
title: Crispy Asian Eggplant & Carrot Noodle Salad with Tangy Lemon Dressing & Crispy Shallots
description: Eggplant is known in our storybooks as the veggie ruler! Dress it in the finest sweet and soy flavours with a golden
crispy glow and marvel at the wealth of flavour the carrot noodle salad brings with gems such as ponzu and a lemon
dressing. We bow before the might of this eggplant dish!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
